:39.000Z","msg":"所謂隱世高手真係得啖笑<br />\n依家咩年代 仲隱到世？<br />\n再講 隱世高手出咗手仲算唔算隱世<br />\n唔出手又點証明佢好打<br />\n<br />\n中國武術 中醫 兩大笑話"},{"pid":"35ba3caf99660a924428a71d1e2183c71958c2f3","tid":60611,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T18:32:17.000Z","msg":"之前有人問散打隊好打 <br />\n定特種部隊好打<br />\n答案係散打隊 <br />\n一日練習量多過特種隊練一個月<br />\n泰臣一年無練拳 已經跌落神壇 點練都上唔返<br />\n你啲國術佬成世都無實戰過<br />\n又無捱過打 練抗擊 一拳就入icu"},{"pid":"d62aed5aa470b9d676ce4961367a32c59c4f90f7","tid":60611,"uid":57346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T18:47:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>所謂隱世高手真係得啖笑<br />\n依家咩年代 仲隱到世？<br />\n再講 隱世高手出咗手仲算唔算隱世<br />\n唔出手又點証明佢好打<br />\n<br />\n中國武術 中醫 兩大笑話</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n雖然覺得風水係迷信，不過聽過蘇民峰講過一樣野好認同，佢話依個世界冇隱世高人，因為相學係相人學返黎既，你成世唔見人重點學睇相？格鬥都係一樣，係對人練架，除非你嫌人類太渣，要入深山探隻熊練，我就冇野好講！"},{"pid":"a49f5e0f2ef408764eae8c8450f4a62dc0d045d3","tid":60611,"uid":59695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T19:12:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>所謂隱世高手真係得啖笑<br />\n依家咩年代 仲隱到世？<br />\n再講 隱世高手出咗手仲算唔算隱世<br />\n唔出手又點証明佢好打<br />\n<br />\n中國武術 中醫 兩大笑話</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n雖然覺得風水係迷信，不過聽過蘇民峰講過一樣野好認同，佢話依個世界冇隱世高人，因為相學係相人學返黎既，你成世唔見人重點學睇相？格鬥都係一樣，係對人練架，除非你嫌人類太渣，要入深山探隻熊練，我就冇野好講！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n閉門講拳應該係所謂中國功夫嘅致命傷，門派之間永無交流，自家拳套路對拆就天下無敵，但係行出街其他人變化少少打埋黎就唔識反應。<br />\n<br />\n而且詠春好興個個徒弟學到唔同嘅「秘技」，唔排除其他門派都係咁，咁嘅過程唔洗三代就成個門派碎片化。<br />\n<br />\n抗打就更唔洗講，我估除咗鐵頭功同鐵春袋之外，無乜係會有抗打練習<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b06c07f86d4cfe8364c00fc3a35fed1c68f10ad8","tid":60611,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T04:41:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>所謂隱世高手真係得啖笑<br />\n依家咩年代 仲隱到世？<br />\n再講 隱世高手出咗手仲算唔算隱世<br />\n唔出手又點証明佢好打<br />\n<br />\n中國武術 中醫 兩大笑話</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n雖然覺得風水係迷信，不過聽過蘇民峰講過一樣野好認同，佢話依個世界冇隱世高人，因為相學係相人學返黎既，你成世唔見人重點學睇相？格鬥都係一樣，係對人練架，除非你嫌人類太渣，要入深山探隻熊練，我就冇野好講！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n閉門講拳應該係所謂中國功夫嘅致命傷，門派之間永無交流，自家拳套路對拆就天下無敵，但係行出街其他人變化少少打埋黎就唔識反應。<br />\n<br />\n而且詠春好興個個徒弟學到唔同嘅「秘技」，唔排除其他門派都係咁，咁嘅過程唔洗三代就成個門派碎片化。<br />\n<br />\n抗打就更唔洗講，我估除咗鐵頭功同鐵春袋之外，無乜係會有抗打練習<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n學拳第一件事係學捱打<br />\n練意志力、身體抗擊同忍痛能力<br />\n唔係人地一拳打中你<br />\n你仲忍緊痛，點還手?"},{"pid":"6a8c119c726e84beeab3632de4bedee8ff821db1","tid":60611,"uid":7034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T04:58:19.000Z","msg":"我覺得武術係古時可能好撚勁 話曬日日練<br />\n但到左而家 個個當興趣班 有撚用咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n古人一日練大半日 而家所謂二十年功力係一星期玩二個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有啲武術技巧其實幾獨到 但要實用就好難下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a8cc9a10306d86ba18e5c4e73959cf63cd62d4f","tid":60611,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T05:01:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌那星支那識唔識拍架？<br />\n<br />\n成日打緊拍啲濕鳩觀眾做乜撚<br />\n<br />\n角度又差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1b7f6ee21f9607e010041e8db2f9ecde5c78cbb","tid":60611,"uid":51546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T05:04:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我覺得題目應該改改<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n應該叫咩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n詠春高手擂台秒殺散打冠軍 全場目瞪口呆</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e5e5690951e710fa85447603451c69896435067","tid":60611,"uid":51546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T05:05:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>真心散打個精神我幾BUY<br />\n實用至上</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實散打係唔係自由搏擊？</blockquote><br />\n武術散打簡稱&ldquo;散打&rdquo;，又叫做&ldquo;散手&rdquo;，喺歷史上有過好多種唔同嘅叫法，好似相搏、手搏、白打、對拆、技擊。散打意思即係將中國武術以實戰為目的所發展出嚟嘅格鬥形式。由於近代散打比賽都係喺擂台上進行，所以又有人叫佢做&ldquo;打擂台&rdquo;"},{"pid":"3e7a19b5c4e5be21f41044a02af4bce0134e2293","tid":60611,"uid":51546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T05:05:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>真正高手唔會出山囉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n起碼唔會上台做節目先，啲謙厚去左邊？仲要唔認輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6f0009d9fe35b215e2749d791e6760a534cfccb","tid":60611,"uid":51546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T05:06:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實詠春好冇我唔知<br />\n或者過去既佢真係好勁<br />\n不過加下好明顯係散打 西洋武學較為優勝</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2ce6bb2eed25e6f4a80f3a56b1391e552f694e6","tid":60611,"uid":51546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T05:09:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>所謂隱世高手真係得啖笑<br />\n依家咩年代 仲隱到世？<br />\n再講 隱世高手出咗手仲算唔算隱世<br />\n唔出手又點証明佢好打<br />\n<br />\n中國武術 中醫 兩大笑話</blockquote><br />\n中國出名多神棍!"},{"pid":"de9daf9aa2a45cab8ddbbd5c9f9c06878584c040","tid":60611,"uid":2485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T05:10:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/8sz6ktjfKLQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F8sz6ktjfKLQ&d=lB94GkTWBmGCjNDwVyBISJkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=220766b5\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/8sz6ktjfKLQ</a><br />\n<br />\n呢個詠春師傅會唔會係最好打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1354d2af522b0058e031f8039c8c308083998c55","tid":60611,"uid":48767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T05:17:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我覺得武術係古時可能好撚勁 話曬日日練<br />\n但到左而家 個個當興趣班 有撚用咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n古人一日練大半日 而家所謂二十年功力係一星期玩二個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有啲武術技巧其實幾獨到 但要實用就好難下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係啊，古人勁到識輕功架"},{"pid":"e99f181436acd3887b683379218ed6359915e3c2","tid":60611,"uid":7034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T05:20:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我覺得武術係古時可能好撚勁 話曬日日練<br />\n但到左而家 個個當興趣班 有撚用咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n古人一日練大半日 而家所謂二十年功力係一星期玩二個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有啲武術技巧其實幾獨到 但要實用就好難下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係啊，古人勁到識輕功架</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n嗰啲輕功咪好似而家跑酷咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faf8681de9357edd5a8484245005edf382b6c434","tid":60611,"uid":44898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T05:34:30.000Z","msg":"請真，有了解中國正史，多朝戰爭同古代社會文化，同埋武俠小說出現年代<br />\n<br />\n都明白根本無中華武術依樣野<br />\n咩內功，外功根本係清末同民國吹出泥。<br />\n<br />\n可惜，好多人都呃自己信有武學存在"},{"pid":"f1148587c080255b6d54cd4d3fae9862cff38b6a","tid":60611,"uid":24034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T05:45:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n雖然覺得風水係迷信，不過聽過蘇民峰講過一樣野好認同，佢話依個世界冇隱世高人，因為相學係相人學返黎既，你成世唔見人重點學睇相？格鬥都係一樣，係對人練架，除非你嫌人類太渣，要入深山探隻熊練，我就冇野好講！</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n閉門講拳應該係所謂中國功夫嘅致命傷，門派之間永無交流，自家拳套路對拆就天下無敵，但係行出街其他人變化少少打埋黎就唔識反應。<br />\n<br />\n而且詠春好興個個徒弟學到唔同嘅「秘技」，唔排除其他門派都係咁，咁嘅過程唔洗三代就成個門派碎片化。<br />\n<br />\n抗打就更唔洗講，我估除咗鐵頭功同鐵春袋之外，無乜係會有抗打練習<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">學拳第一件事係學捱打</span><br />\n練意志力、身體抗擊同忍痛能力<br />\n唔係人地一拳打中你<br />\n你仲忍緊痛，點還手?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},{"pid":"12addc703504389e803ff405c208ae682cb6f6a8","tid":60611,"uid":51546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T05:54:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>請真，有了解中國正史，多朝戰爭同古代社會文化，同埋武俠小說出現年代<br />\n<br />\n都明白根本無中華武術依樣野<br />\n咩內功，外功根本係清末同民國吹出泥。<br />\n<br />\n可惜，好多人都呃自己信有武學存在</blockquote><br />\n中華文化=清朝文化"},{"pid":"074aa5732f3409450053a6f3ec905f097cef6c53","tid":60611,"uid":39855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T05:59:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>真心散打個精神我幾BUY<br />\n實用至上</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實散打係唔係自由搏擊？</blockquote><br />\n武術散打簡稱&ldquo;散打&rdquo;，又叫做&ldquo;散手&rdquo;，喺歷史上有過好多種唔同嘅叫法，好似相搏、手搏、白打、對拆、技擊。散打意思即係將中國武術以實戰為目的所發展出嚟嘅格鬥形式。由於近代散打比賽都係喺擂台上進行，所以又有人叫佢做&ldquo;打擂台&rdquo;</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n成段大部分都係鳩up"},{"pid":"77b48b969113113b3ab958a372feee305914cf0f","tid":60611,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T06:03:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n閉門講拳應該係所謂中國功夫嘅致命傷，門派之間永無交流，自家拳套路對拆就天下無敵，但係行出街其他人變化少少打埋黎就唔識反應。<br />\n<br />\n而且詠春好興個個徒弟學到唔同嘅「秘技」，唔排除其他門派都係咁，咁嘅過程唔洗三代就成個門派碎片化。<br />\n<br />\n抗打就更唔洗講，我估除咗鐵頭功同鐵春袋之外，無乜係會有抗打練習<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">學拳第一件事係學捱打</span><br />\n練意志力、身體抗擊同忍痛能力<br />\n唔係人地一拳打中你<br />\n你仲忍緊痛，點還手?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n認真，就算打人，隻手都會好痛，所以要不停打不停打，打到一拳打落牆都冇反應先得"},{"pid":"9